require cni [ kind="main" ]

DESCRIPTION="This simple plugin will move the requested device from the host’s network namespace to the container’s. IPAM configuration can be used for this plugin. This plugin can also be used for a device bound to dpdk driver via pciBusID or runtimeConfig deviceID parameter then IPAM configuration will be ignored."
PLATFORMS="~amd64"
